@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### Obtener todos los cursos
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/courses

###

### Obtener curso por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/courses/1

###

### Crear curso
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/courses
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Matematicas",
  "description": "Curso de matematicas avanzadas",
  "teacher": "Juan Perez",
  "group_id": 1,
  "status": "active"
}

###

### Actualizar curso
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/courses/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Matematicas Actualizado",
  "status": "active"
}

###

### Eliminar curso fisicamente
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/courses/1

###

### Eliminar curso logicamente
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/courses/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "inactive"
}
